name: Joybound People & Pets - Free Pet Food
description: Free pet food for residents who need assistance
fullDescription: Joybound's pet food assistance program helps Contra Costa County families keep their pets by providing free food during financial hardship.
whatTheyOffer:
- Free dog food
- Free cat food
- Pet supplies when available
- No-judgment assistance
- Helps prevent pet surrender due to cost
howToGetIt:
1. Must be a Contra Costa County resident
2. Contact Joybound to request assistance
3. Provide basic information about your pets
4. Arrange pickup or delivery of food
